title: Australian diary. No. 039
creator_credit: Australian National Film Board and Jack S. Allan
brief_description: A poultry farm at Werribbe Victoria is shown producing eggs by the million. The latest design for a three way hat designed by Australian milliner John Pickworth ius revealed. Baby animlas at Taronga Park Zoo are favourites. The process of reclaiming salt from the sea and a salt refinery in South Australia are shown. Big game fishing - shark and marlin are caught near Sydney.
